{"tid":616902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"挨酸比女神妹醜！有村藍里狠砸100萬日元「切牙肉+拔6顆牙」","createTime":"2018-04-04T14:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T07:57:51.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7430fa62bf407c5370f7f5cabc199ff91a2563a5","tid":616902,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3196/d3196327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3196%2Fd3196327.jpg&h=64d37e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲有村藍里是新生代女神有村架純的親姊姊，顏值常被網友酸醜。<br />\n<br />\n日本寫真女星有村藍里是有村架純的親姊姊，自從被爆出姊妹關係後，長期被網友批評沒有妹妹漂亮，姊妹倆人氣天差地遠。她近日參加節目錄影，公開認了拔掉6顆牙、燒掉牙肉重新改造。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3196/d3196321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3196%2Fd3196321.jpg&h=a2bc77f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有村藍里拍寫真出道，後來被曝光是有村架純姊姊。<br />\n<br />\n現年27歲的有村藍里參加《中居之窗》的「醜女特集」，自爆顏值常被網友拿去和妹妹比較，「最常被說嘴巴很醜，其實我已經拔掉6顆牙齒矯正過了。」但是她認為矯正說嘴巴還是有問題，「第一次說這種事，我把牙肉削掉了。」她表示自己一笑就會露出牙齦、還被說像猩猩，於是把牙肉燒了切掉，減少「猩猩感」，嘴巴重新塑型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3196/d3196322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3196%2Fd3196322.jpg&h=2c337017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有村藍里說曾被網友形容像猩猩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3196/d3196324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3196%2Fd3196324.jpg&h=ea5c7990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有村藍里不但拔了6顆牙，還去切牙肉，重新塑型。<br />\n<br />\n當主持人中居正廣問「這是整型的一種嗎？」有村藍里強調，「牙齒不是整型，我認為是矯正。」她等上3個月重新長出牙肉，再加上全瓷牙齒美容，共計花費日幣100萬元（約台幣28萬），足以彌補與5.2公升V12雙Turbo頂級版（608ps馬力、71.4kgm扭力）的動力差距。如今在鏡頭前露出白牙笑說：「總算可以變漂亮可愛一點了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3196/d3196326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3196%2Fd3196326.jpg&h=a8797eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有村藍里分享矯正前照片，一笑就露出牙齦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3196/d3196325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3196%2Fd3196325.jpg&h=26f6790e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有村藍里還做了全瓷美容。"},{"pid":"12180be999353da5205487826c8847a942a6f1dc","tid":616902,"uid":5587,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"再加上全瓷牙齒美容，共計花費日幣100萬元（約台幣28萬），足以彌補與5.2公升V12雙Turbo頂級版（608ps馬力、71.4kgm扭力）的動力差距。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d238871706398f96301065a231db5e0e75ea0c01","tid":616902,"uid":121911,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"12180be999353da5205487826c8847a942a6f1dc","tid":616902,"uid":5587,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"再加上全瓷牙齒美容，共計花費日幣100萬元（約台幣28萬），足以彌補與5.2公升V12雙Turbo頂級版（608ps馬力、71.4kgm扭力）的動力差距。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 棚牙都有咁大馬力 比佢含咪爽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157a6d664dcf52bf700c2132dfaefe20f973f1fa","tid":616902,"uid":37989,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"d238871706398f96301065a231db5e0e75ea0c01","tid":616902,"uid":121911,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"12180be999353da5205487826c8847a942a6f1dc","tid":616902,"uid":5587,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"再加上全瓷牙齒美容，共計花費日幣100萬元（約台幣28萬），足以彌補與5.2公升V12雙Turbo頂級版（608ps馬力、71.4kgm扭力）的動力差距。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/fac